No. 11-408. David H. Tullis and Michael S. Mack, Petitioners v. UMB Bank, N.A., et al. 565 U.S. 1148, 132 S. Ct. 1005,

181 L. Ed. 2d 791,

2012 U.S. LEXIS 499. January 9, 2012.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.

Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 423 Fed. Appx. 567.
